Not a recipe. This file lists the dairy items typically bought every week. Include it alongside real recipes when generating a shopping list so these staples appear automatically — useful as a workaround for the Cook iOS app, which doesn't support adding ad-hoc items.

Buy: @full fat milk{1%l}, @skimmed milk{1%l}, @plain rahka{250%g}, @flavoured rahka{250%g}, and @greek yogurt{500%g}.
